    {
      "segment_id": 11,
      "original_text": "מְנָא לַן? אִיבָּעֵית אֵימָא מִדְּאִיצְטְרִיךְ קְרָא לְמַעוֹטַהּ. וְאִיבָּעֵית אֵימָא דְּאָמַר קְרָא: ״וּבִגְדֵי הַקֹּדֶשׁ אֲשֶׁר לְאַהֲרֹן יִהְיוּ לְבָנָיו אַחֲרָיו לְמׇשְׁחָה בָהֶם וּלְמַלֵּא בָם אֶת יָדָם״, אִיתַּקַּשׁ מְשִׁיחָה לְרִיבּוּי: מָה רִיבּוּי שִׁבְעָה, אַף מְשִׁיחָה שִׁבְעָה.",
      "reconstructed_text": "מְנָא לַן? אִיבָּעֵית אֵימָא מִדְּאִיצְטְרִיךְ קְרָא לְמַעוֹטַהּ. וְאִיבָּעֵית אֵימָא דְּאָמַר קְרָא: בָהֶם וּלְמַלֵּא בָם אֶת יָדָם״, אִיתַּקַּשׁ מְשִׁיחָה לְרִיבּוּי: מָה רִיבּוּי שִׁבְעָה, אַף מְשִׁיחָה שִׁבְעָה.",
      "reconstructed_html": "מְנָא לַן? אִיבָּעֵית אֵימָא מִדְּאִיצְטְרִיךְ קְרָא לְמַעוֹטַהּ. וְאִיבָּעֵית אֵימָא דְּאָמַר קְרָא: <span class=\"girsa-change girsa-deletion\" data-change-type=\"deletion\" data-confidence=\"high\" data-source=\"rashi_girsa\" data-source-ref=\"Rashi on Yoma 5a:8:3\" data-marker=\"ל&quot;ג\" data-original=\"״וּבִגְדֵי\">״וּבִגְדֵי</span> <span class=\"girsa-change girsa-deletion\" data-change-type=\"deletion\" data-confidence=\"high\" data-source=\"rashi_girsa\" data-source-ref=\"Rashi on Yoma 5a:8:3\" data-marker=\"ל&quot;ג\" data-original=\"הַקֹּדֶשׁ\">הַקֹּדֶשׁ</span> <span class=\"girsa-change girsa-deletion\" data-change-type=\"deletion\" data-confidence=\"high\" data-source=\"rashi_girsa\" data-source-ref=\"Rashi on Yoma 5a:8:3\" data-marker=\"ל&quot;ג\" data-original=\"אֲשֶׁר\">אֲשֶׁר</span> <span class=\"girsa-change girsa-deletion\" data-change-type=\"deletion\" data-confidence=\"high\" data-source=\"rashi_girsa\" data-source-ref=\"Rashi on Yoma 5a:8:3\" data-marker=\"ל&quot;ג\" data-original=\"לְאַהֲרֹן\">לְאַהֲרֹן</span> <span class=\"girsa-change girsa-deletion\" data-change-type=\"deletion\" data-confidence=\"high\" data-source=\"rashi_girsa\" data-source-ref=\"Rashi on Yoma 5a:8:3\" data-marker=\"ל&quot;ג\" data-original=\"יִהְיוּ\">יִהְיוּ</span> <span class=\"girsa-change girsa-deletion\" data-change-type=\"deletion\" data-confidence=\"high\" data-source=\"rashi_girsa\" data-source-ref=\"Rashi on Yoma 5a:8:3\" data-marker=\"ל&quot;ג\" data-original=\"לְבָנָיו\">לְבָנָיו</span> <span class=\"girsa-change girsa-deletion\" data-change-type=\"deletion\" data-confidence=\"high\" data-source=\"rashi_girsa\" data-source-ref=\"Rashi on Yoma 5a:8:3\" data-marker=\"ל&quot;ג\" data-original=\"אַחֲרָיו\">אַחֲרָיו</span> <span class=\"girsa-change girsa-deletion\" data-change-type=\"deletion\" data-confidence=\"high\" data-source=\"rashi_girsa\" data-source-ref=\"Rashi on Yoma 5a:8:3\" data-marker=\"ל&quot;ג\" data-original=\"לְמׇשׁ